msgid "Scenario IV: Return to Blood on the Altar"
msgstr "冒险IV：重返血色祭坛"

msgid "Remove the original Village Commons location from the game. Put the new Village Commons <i>(Silent Decay)</i> into play. Each investigator begins play at the Village Commons <i>(Silent Decay)</i>."
msgstr "将原版的公共空地地点移出游戏，用新版的公共空地<i>(寂静荒地)</i>地点替换。每位调查员从公共空地<i>(寂静荒地)</i>开始游戏。"

msgid "Add the new locations to the original locations from the <i>Blood on the Altar</i> encounter set. Remove two of the three copies of each location from the game at random. Then, choose one of the six remaining locations at random, and remove it from the game as well. Put the remaining five locations into play."
msgstr "将新的地点加入<i>血色祭坛</i>遭遇组原有的地点之中。随机将每种地点(各3张)中的各2张移出游戏。然后，随机从剩余的6个地点中选择1个，将其移出游戏。将剩余地点放置入场。"

msgid "Set the following cards aside, out of play: Hired Gun, Silas Bishop, The Hidden Chamber, Key to the Chamber, and Powder of Ibn-Ghazi."
msgstr "将下列卡牌放在一边，位于场外：受雇枪手、塞拉斯·毕晓普、隐藏密室、密室的钥匙、伊本巴奇之粉末。"

msgid "Seeking vengeance, the gang from the Clover Club has followed you to Dunwich. Gather all cards from the <i>Naomi’s Crew</i> encounter set."
msgstr "欧巴尼恩帮决定对你复仇，他们派出打手，一路跟踪你到敦威治。找出<i>娜奥米的打手</i>遭遇组。"

msgid "Do not shuffle these cards into the encounter deck yet."
msgstr "暂时不要将这些卡牌洗入遭遇牌堆。"

msgid "Before shuffling the <i>Naomi's Crew</i> encounter set into the encounter deck, take the previously set-aside The Hidden Chamber and Key to the Chamber cards, along with the top 3 cards of the encounter deck. Shuffle them and randomly deal 1 card facedown underneath each location in play except Village Commons."
msgstr "在将<i>娜奥米的打手</i>遭遇组洗入遭遇牌堆之前，将放在一边的隐藏密室和密室的钥匙，以及遭遇牌堆顶部3张卡牌混洗。面朝下，在除公共空地以外每张地点卡下各放置1张。"

msgid "Spawn one set-aside Hired Gun at one of the locations not connected to Village Commons. Shuffle the other set-aside Hired Gun, along with the rest of the <i>Naomi's Crew</i> encounter set into the encounter deck."
msgstr "将放在一边的1张受雇枪手生成在没有连接到公共空地的地点。将放在一边的其余的受雇枪手，以及<i>娜奥米的打手</i>遭遇组中剩余的卡牌洗入遭遇牌堆。"
